{"tid":1287072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】急症室醫生︰ 求求你們不要輕生","createTime":"2019-07-05T05:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T05:42:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b90789612b839193c286b54f221cb7c973f86ec","tid":1287072,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"自修訂《逃犯條例》引發連串爭議，暴力畫面和社會氛圍引致部分人有情緒問題，甚至有輕生個案。有急症室醫生在facebook專頁發文，以醫生叔叔為下款，表示為年輕人擔憂，呼籲大家珍惜生命，不要輕生，因政府不會再有任何改變。<br />\n<br />\n有逾4萬網民追蹤的《Dr. Ray 的急症室迎送生涯》facebook專頁，昨晚（4日）發帖文，指自己明白一眾年青人「心很累」和有很強的無力感，全文如下：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">弟弟妹妹們：\n\n聽醫生叔叔的話，求求你們，千萬不要自殺了。\n\n或者你會覺得，自己做甚麼都沒有用，倒不如用死諫來醒悟人心吧。\n\n已經犧牲了四個人，要醒的人都已經醒了，而[red]裝睡的人是永遠都叫不醒的[/red]。\n\n[red][size=5]同伴愈少，聲音也會愈小，政府只會覺得又少一個暴徒而已，不會有任何改變的。[/size=5][/red]\n\n各位弟弟妹妹們，叔叔也有很大的無力感，心也很累。\n\n[red]七月一日當晚，我很擔心你們，知道你們全部都走了的時候，我忍不住哭了。[/red]\n\n弟弟妹妹，你們[red]一個都不能少[/red]；叔叔將來就是要交棒給你們了。\n\n所以，求求各位，[red]珍惜生命，千萬不要再輕生了[/red]。\n\n醫生叔叔</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dr.ray.on.call/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdr.ray.on.call%2F&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=0aea7f2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dr.ray.on.call/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2393003/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2393003%2F&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=792cb4b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2393003/</a>"},{"pid":"b1e0ad164a885ee5f8128819b85734950bdb8054","tid":1287072,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwzHtt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwzHtt9.jpg&h=c3875f24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b997a35cdbf607334b766e387cad09b894841116","tid":1287072,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7VSQHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7VSQHT.jpg&h=ddd5da5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/speakforthetruth/photos/a.298448867016863/1090124344515974/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fspeakforthetruth%2Fphotos%2Fa.298448867016863%2F1090124344515974%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=51a5575f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/speakforthetruth/photos/a.298448867016863/1090124344515974/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"658ffb62c36bc0f61e554d0e69b495258b41f5d1","tid":1287072,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f4a1a4d8380531ec517ccd24e3bec893b77e22","tid":1287072,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"fa83965cea4cb3f698d5bef8e1bb9d9b4ad7b42e","tid":1287072,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae069a8fb2f50e0d28908c1f652713e7f44fb66","tid":1287072,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}